c: 65
v: 2
t: "Ngakho-ke uma sebesigcwalisekisile isikhathi sabo sokulinda, manjalo babambeni ngendlela enhle (esemthethweni) noma nibadedele abesifazane ngendlela enhle, futhi nibabizele ofakazi ababili abanobulungiswa phakathi kwenu futhi nenzele uMvelinqangi ubufakazi, lokho uyala ngako noma ngabe ngubani okholwa kuMvelinqangi nasosukwini lokugcina, futhi noma ngabe ngubani owesaba uMvelinqangi umenzela indlela ephumayo"